+// ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
+// Walk-cycle tuning.
+//
+// A natural human gait is ~2 steps/second; each step alternates L/R so the
+// sine wave frequency we want is STEP_HZ = ~2.2. We multiply by 2π to
+// convert to rad/s for the sin() argument.
